desktop-waifu (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New features in this release:
  * Conversation Export - Export chat history to JSON or Markdown
  * Message Context Menu - Hover to copy or edit & retry messages
  * Slash Commands - /clear, /settings, /character with autocomplete
  * Streaming Responses - Real-time typewriter effect for LLM responses
  * Global Hotkeys - Super+M to toggle overlay visibility
  * Clipboard Integration - Paste images for vision models (Ctrl+V)
  * Desktop Notifications - Configurable notifications for responses

 -- yv-was-taken <yvmail@proton.me>  Sun, 25 Jan 2026 00:07:20 -0600

